Chicago, April 20, 1997<br><br>
Dear friends:<br><br>
I would like to thank all of you to be interested in the Vietnam War. I just came here for about three years and I  think that many American still do not understand about the Vietnam war.  I will ask some Vietnamese organizations or former veterans in Chicago if they have information and film that can help some of you understand more about the war.<br><br>
Thank you very much!<br>
Especially Thanks to this Web site www.pbs.org for sharing information about the Vietnam War.<br><br>
